OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1777554668
OL,3,CSanquhar residents prepare for
OL,4,C'devastating' 50-mile diversion in town
OL,6,FResidents in Sanquhar are preparing
OL,7,Ffor a "devastating" 50-mile diversion
OL,8,Fto get in and out of the town.
OL,10,FBusiness owners say they are bracing
OL,11,Fthemselves for the partial closure of
OL,12,Fthe A76 in June and July as work to
OL,13,Frepair the Sanquhar Tolbooth Museum
OL,14,Ftakes place.
OL,16,FThe six-week closure will see numerous
OL,17,Fdiversions in place around the town.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
