FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1777554668
OL,3,CSanquhar residents prepare for
OL,4,C'devastating' 50-mile diversion in town
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Border, local
OL,7,Fpostmaster Barry Ford said the work
OL,8,Fcould lead to the first ever closure
OL,9,Fof his Post Office.
OL,11,FHe said: "The footfall is definitely
OL,12,Fgoing to drop and we are going to have
OL,13,Fto assess it to see whether it is
OL,14,Fgoing to be viable or not.
OL,16,F"We have never shut in the 320 years
OL,17,Fthat the Post Office has been open but
OL,18,Fone of the options, if it gets too
OL,19,Fexpensive, is that we may have to
OL,20,Fclose down.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1777554668
OL,3,CSanquhar residents prepare for
OL,4,C'devastating' 50-mile diversion in town
OL,6,F"It is a hypothetical thing at the
OL,7,Fmoment but it is definitely going to
OL,8,Faffect us."
OL,10,FCharlie Brown owns the newsagent in
OL,11,Fthe town and believes the closure will
OL,12,Fhave a serious detrimental knock-on
OL,13,Fimpact.
OL,15,FHe said: "It is going to be
OL,16,Fdevastating for us. The street is a
OL,17,Flot quieter than it used to be anyway,
OL,18,Fas it is everywhere.
OL,20,F"It is really going to devastate
OL,21,FSanquhar, six weeks is a long time.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1777554668
OL,3,CSanquhar residents prepare for
OL,4,C'devastating' 50-mile diversion in town
OL,6,F"I can see what the council are trying
OL,7,Fto do an I believe they are trying to
OL,8,Fhelp."
OL,10,FThe local authority says the work to
OL,11,Fthe tolbooth is essential and they
OL,12,Fhave considered other options but
OL,13,Fbelieve the one chosen had the safest
OL,14,Fworking environment and the best long
OL,15,Fterm outcome for the building.
OL,16,FDumfries and Galloway council also
OL,17,Fconfirmed the museum inside will
OL,18,Fremain open during the works.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
